Zach: So the machine queen sends her prophet.
Player: This doesn’t have to end in blood.
Zach: Peace is just war where only one side remembers losing.
Nataly: You ordered the purge. You closed the libraries. You turned magic into a weapon.
Zach: Magic is a weapon. Karol forgot that. Fini believed she could tame it.
Zach: And look where that faith led.
Player: You’re wrong.
Zach: Well then prove it, GUARDS!
